```plantuml
@startuml IBMDeveloperMEA_YPDL-Recurrent-Neural-Networks-using-TensorFlow-Keras

actor User
participant "Jupyter Notebook" as Notebook
participant "LSTM Model" as Model
participant "Embedding Layer" as Embedding
participant "Dense Layer" as Dense
participant "Penn Treebank Dataset" as Dataset
participant "Training Loop" as Training

User -> Notebook: Executes cells
Notebook -> Dataset: Loads and preprocesses data
Dataset --> Notebook: Returns processed sequences

Notebook -> Model: Initializes LSTM architecture
Model -> Embedding: Adds embedding layer
Model -> Dense: Adds dense layer with softmax

Notebook -> Training: Starts training process
Training -> Model: Feeds training batches
Model -> Embedding: Processes word embeddings
Embedding --> Model: Returns embedded vectors
Model --> Training: Computes predictions
Training -> Model: Backpropagates errors
Model --> Notebook: Returns training metrics

Notebook -> User: Displays training progress\nand evaluation results

@enduml
```